mock_profile = prisma.models.Profile(id='profile-id', name='Test Creator',
    username='creator', description='Test description', links=['link1'],
    avatarUrl='avatar.jpg', isFeatured=False, createdAt=datetime.now(),
    updatedAt=datetime.now())

    mock_profile)

    mock_profile)

    'Test description', links=['link1'], avatar_url='avatar.jpg',
    is_featured=False)
result = await db.update_or_create_profile('user-id', profile)
